trans-unit.source: Provides a XAML type system identifier representation for attachable members.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma representação de identificador de sistema de tipo XAML para membros anexáveis.

trans-unit.source: The identifier structure parallels the <paramref name="declaringType" /><see langword="." /><paramref name="memberName" /> string form for attachable member usage.
trans-unit.target: A estrutura do identificador coloca em paralelo o formulário de cadeia de caracteres <paramref name="declaringType" /><see langword="." /><paramref name="memberName" /> para uso do membro anexável.

trans-unit.source: The <c>declaringType</c> component of the identifier, which should match the name of the declaring <see cref="P:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Type" />.
trans-unit.target: O componente <c>declaringType</c> do identificador, que deve corresponder ao nome do <see cref="P:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Type" /> declarante.

trans-unit.source: The <c>memberName</c> component of the identifier, which should match the <see cref="P:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Name" />.
trans-unit.target: O <c>memberName</c> componente do identificador, que deve corresponder ao <see cref="P:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Name" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <paramref name="declaringType" /> component value of the <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor de componente <paramref name="declaringType" /> de <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="declaringType" /> component value of the <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="declaringType" /> valor de componente de <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.DeclaringType%2A> value should match the name of the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Type%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> of the attachable member's XAML type system information.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.DeclaringType%2A> valor deve corresponder ao nome do <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Type%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> de XAML do membro anexável informações de tipo de sistema.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether two <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> objects have the same value.
trans-unit.target: Determina se dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> têm o mesmo valor.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with the current <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado com o <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether this instance of <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> and a specified object have the same value.
trans-unit.target: Determina se essa instância do <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> e um objeto especificado têm o mesmo valor.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is an <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> and if its value is the same as this instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="obj" /> for um <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> e seu valor for o mesmo que o dessa instância; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> to compare with the current <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> a ser comparado com o <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether this instance and another specified <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> object have the same value.
trans-unit.target: Determina se essa instância e outro objeto <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> especificado têm o mesmo valor.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the objects have the same value; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se ambos os objetos tiverem o mesmo valor; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The values that this method checks for equality are <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.DeclaringType%2A> and <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.MemberName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Os valores que esse método verifica a igualdade são <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.DeclaringType%2A> e <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.MemberName%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash para este <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: An integer hash code.
trans-unit.target: Um código hash inteiro.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <paramref name="memberName" /> component value of the <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor de componente <paramref name="memberName" /> de <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="memberName" /> component value of the <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="memberName" /> valor de componente de <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.MemberName%2A> value should match the <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Name%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> of the attachable member's XAML type system information.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier.MemberName%2A> valor deve corresponder a <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember.Name%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> de XAML do membro anexável informações de tipo de sistema.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />, or <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> ou <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />, or <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> ou <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether two specified <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> objects have the same value.
trans-unit.target: Determina se dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> especificados têm o mesmo valor.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of <paramref name="left" /> is the same as the value of <paramref name="right" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o valor de <paramref name="left" /> for o mesmo que o valor de <paramref name="right" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />, or <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> ou <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />, or <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> ou <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether two specified <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> objects have different values.
trans-unit.target: Determina se dois objetos <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> especificados têm valores diferentes.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of <paramref name="left" /> differs from the value of <paramref name="right" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o valor de <paramref name="left" /> for diferente do valor de <paramref name="right" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the current <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que representa o <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that represents the current <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que representa o <see cref="T:System.Xaml.AttachableMemberIdentifier" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: This implementation returns a string form that parallels the XAML attachable member usage in markup.
trans-unit.target: Essa implementação retorna um formulário de cadeia de caracteres paralela a XAML anexável marcação de uso.

trans-unit.source: That string form is `declaringType.memberName`.
trans-unit.target: Se o formulário de cadeia de caracteres é `declaringType.memberName`.
